[Russian continues]

21:57.657 --> 21:59.024
[Speaks Russian]

21:59.759 --> 22:02.733
_

22:04.373 --> 22:07.734
_

22:07.734 --> 22:11.036
- [Continues speaking Russian]
- Shh.

22:22.682 --> 22:24.550
[Inhales sharply]

22:29.756 --> 22:32.224
- [Exhales]
- Now we test the vaccine.

22:35.138 --> 22:38.374
_

22:40.061 --> 22:43.699
_

22:43.700 --> 22:46.569
_

22:46.594 --> 22:48.398
_

22:48.398 --> 22:49.975
[Shouting in Russian]

22:50.009 --> 22:52.911
What are you waiting for? Do it.

22:52.946 --> 22:54.379
[Panting]

22:58.985 --> 23:03.288
- Aah!
- [Shouting in Russian]

23:03.323 --> 23:08.260
[Muttering]

23:08.294 --> 23:11.430
Aah!

23:11.498 --> 23:13.398
[Exhales]

23:13.433 --> 23:14.697
[Motor revving]

23:14.697 --> 23:17.603
Man: Whiskey frog, 1 back
9. Whiskey frog, 1 back 9.

23:17.637 --> 23:19.037
Standing by.

23:19.072 --> 23:21.740
Outstanding.

23:21.774 --> 23:23.976
Let's hope she got him that note.

23:25.578 --> 23:30.048
[Speaking Russian, laughing]

23:30.083 --> 23:32.417
Comfortable?

23:32.452 --> 23:34.953
As a boy, I shared a room
not much larger than this

23:34.988 --> 23:36.889
with my five brothers and sisters.

23:36.923 --> 23:40.392
My parents were not
among the political elite.

23:40.426 --> 23:43.061
We grew familiar with tight quarters,

23:43.129 --> 23:44.897
with cold, with hunger.

23:44.964 --> 23:48.300
Oh, that's a real sob story. Well told.

23:48.334 --> 23:50.135
Aren't they expecting
you back in Transylvania

23:50.169 --> 23:52.104
- before sunrise?
- [Chuckles]

23:54.941 --> 23:59.411
This vaccine your Dr. Scott has developed

23:59.445 --> 24:02.347
is now the single greatest
commodity in the world.

24:02.382 --> 24:05.117
Every day its value increases,

24:05.151 --> 24:08.253
as those not yet infected
grow desperate for it.

24:08.288 --> 24:11.156
And it's mine! [Laughs]

24:11.190 --> 24:14.426
The American Dream.
Isn't that the expression?

24:14.460 --> 24:17.729
Think it got lost in the translation.

24:17.764 --> 24:21.266
Once I have successfully
tested the vaccine,

24:21.334 --> 24:26.672
I will most likely kill all
of you and destroy your ship.

24:26.706 --> 24:31.076
But... perhaps there's another way...

24:31.110 --> 24:33.679
A way that can help your
shipmates, your friends,

24:33.746 --> 24:36.515
your families.

24:36.549 --> 24:40.786
You have courage, first-rate ship,

24:40.820 --> 24:44.389
a crew that will follow
you wherever you say.

24:44.424 --> 24:48.360
I think we can work well together.

24:48.394 --> 24:51.964
Achieve a great deal together.

24:58.104 --> 25:00.305
My name is Thomas Chandler,

25:00.340 --> 25:03.108
Commander, United States Navy,

25:03.176 --> 25:08.547
serial number 4242022634.

25:10.984 --> 25:13.852
Tex: Was a good talk, Boris.

25:13.886 --> 25:15.988
If there's nothing else... [Inhales]

25:16.022 --> 25:19.024
Well, we'd like to get some shut-eye.

25:25.531 --> 25:26.999
10 minutes, sir.

25:27.033 --> 25:28.600
Master Chief, how you feeling?

25:28.635 --> 25:30.168
Scared to death, sir.

25:30.236 --> 25:32.537
Well, you're not alone, I'm sure.

25:32.605 --> 25:35.607
No, sir. I am not.

25:35.642 --> 25:36.875
Yeah.

25:38.878 --> 25:40.679
[Sighs]

25:42.315 --> 25:43.749
[Radio chirps]

25:43.783 --> 25:46.385
This is your X.O.

25:47.954 --> 25:49.721
So...

25:52.458 --> 25:54.192
Two sailors walk into a bar.

25:57.897 --> 25:59.665
And they both walk out.

26:02.702 --> 26:04.703
We will get our men back.

26:04.771 --> 26:06.872
We will get our captain back.

26:06.906 --> 26:08.440
That is all.

26:08.474 --> 26:09.975
[Radio chirps]

26:13.613 --> 26:16.048
Maneuver the ship into position
to pick up the extract team.

26:16.115 --> 26:17.783
Aye, sir.

26:18.985 --> 26:20.752
Thought I'd open with a joke.

26:20.787 --> 26:22.454
It was a good one, sir.

26:30.904 --> 26:32.389
_

26:32.390 --> 26:34.718
_

26:40.640 --> 26:42.641
- [Thud]
- [Grunts]

26:44.577 --> 26:45.977
[Grunts]

26:46.012 --> 26:47.746
[Panting]

26:47.780 --> 26:49.147
Now you can kiss my ass.

26:49.215 --> 26:52.517
[Gasping, choking]

26:52.552 --> 26:55.120
[Body thuds, keys rattle]

26:57.123 --> 26:58.390
[Lock clicks]

27:03.816 --> 27:05.884
[Man speaks in Russian]

27:05.952 --> 27:07.686
[Grunts]

27:07.720 --> 27:10.222
[All grunting]

27:19.732 --> 27:21.366
[Grunts loudly]

27:23.236 --> 27:24.603
[Body thuds]

27:31.187 --> 27:35.035
Mm. I don't wish to
ruin the ending for you,

27:35.035 --> 27:37.894
but your vaccine will not work.

27:38.861 --> 27:40.695
Isn't that right, Dimitri?

27:40.730 --> 27:43.098
You're not feeling so good, huh?

27:43.132 --> 27:45.867
The virus already has you in its clutches.

28:07.056 --> 28:09.924
[Breathing heavily]

28:12.695 --> 28:15.497
[Footsteps approaching]

28:15.564 --> 28:17.432
The cavalry has arrived.

28:17.466 --> 28:19.067
You okay, sir?

28:19.101 --> 28:21.236
I'm fine. This your idea, Burk?

28:21.270 --> 28:23.838
Can't take all the credit,
but I'm happy to be here, sir.

28:23.873 --> 28:26.007
Yeah. We'll talk about this later.

28:26.042 --> 28:27.609
Where's Dr. Scott?

28:27.643 --> 28:29.844
The lab should be one level down, back aft.

28:29.879 --> 28:31.513
We'll pick her up on the
way to the extract point,

28:31.547 --> 28:33.014
- off the flight deck.
- Let's move.

28:52.101 --> 28:53.468
[Clicks, beeps]

28:59.975 --> 29:01.443
Like clockwork.

29:11.353 --> 29:14.122
[Beep, electronic whine]

29:15.791 --> 29:17.559
Danny: [Whispering] Stingray,
this is Tiger Shark.

29:17.593 --> 29:19.761
Rally point one is a go. Package in hand.

29:19.795 --> 29:22.197
- Moving to rally point two. How copy?
- Copy that.

29:22.264 --> 29:24.365
No, sir, lab is...

29:24.400 --> 29:26.401
Sir, lab is this way.

29:28.537 --> 29:30.572
Captain, this is officer country.

29:30.606 --> 29:32.740
<i>Sir? Sir?</i>

29:32.775 --> 29:34.242
Sir, what are you looking for?

29:34.276 --> 29:35.810
Asmik.

29:39.281 --> 29:41.683
You want off this ship,
come with me right now.

29:41.717 --> 29:44.119
[Panting]

29:56.365 --> 29:59.601
Cossetti, Cruz, I want
you to escort Mrs. Tophet

29:59.635 --> 30:01.743
and her daughter to
the extraction point.

30:01.768 --> 30:02.370
Yes, sir.

30:02.371 --> 30:06.307
Rest of you, with me. We're
going to get Dr. Scott.

30:13.835 --> 30:15.303
_

