30:37.106 --> 30:39.040
[Whispering] Clear!

30:41.510 --> 30:42.810
[Exhales, mutters]

30:45.614 --> 30:48.216
- [Beep, electronic whine]
- [Exhales]

30:48.250 --> 30:52.220
[Whispering in Russian]

30:53.689 --> 30:55.223
[Whispering in Russian continues]

30:55.257 --> 30:56.691
[Speaks Russian]

31:06.735 --> 31:08.336
- [Speaks Russian]
- [Door closes]

31:08.370 --> 31:10.171
You come with me... now.

31:10.206 --> 31:12.941
Nikolai... [Speaks Russian]

31:19.381 --> 31:22.584
But I still need to give him
the second part of his vaccine.

31:22.618 --> 31:25.553
Admiral wants you. You
must come with me now.

31:25.588 --> 31:29.224
But if we leave the room
and the vaccine test fails,

31:29.291 --> 31:33.628
Ruskov will kill both me and you.

31:42.504 --> 31:44.572
Do it. Quick.

31:46.575 --> 31:48.176
[Latches click]

32:10.299 --> 32:13.735
[Clattering]

32:20.576 --> 32:22.910
[Gunshot]

32:22.945 --> 32:24.312
[Gasping]

32:26.949 --> 32:29.450
[Shouting in Russian]

32:29.485 --> 32:31.286
No! Hey, hey... Pierce the plastic,

32:31.320 --> 32:34.455
everyone on this ship dies... You first.

32:34.490 --> 32:36.090
Huh?

32:36.125 --> 32:37.725
- I helped you!
- [Panting]

32:37.760 --> 32:40.094
- [Thud]
- [Gasps]

32:40.129 --> 32:41.763
Ma'am, it's us. Drop your weapon.

32:43.599 --> 32:45.366
Doctor, put the weapon down!

32:50.372 --> 32:52.106
I'll be damned.

32:52.141 --> 32:55.843
[Breathing unevenly]

32:55.878 --> 32:58.946
Dolphin, this is Tiger Shark.
Rally point two is a go.

32:58.981 --> 33:00.181
Shut her down.

33:13.664 --> 33:16.599
[Man speaking Russian]

33:25.209 --> 33:27.644
[Beep, electronic whine]

33:27.711 --> 33:29.279
[Rapid beeps]

33:29.313 --> 33:32.315
[Explosion]

33:32.349 --> 33:33.583
[Rumbling]

33:33.617 --> 33:36.019
Here we go. Move it out.

33:36.053 --> 33:37.787
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

33:37.820 --> 33:40.090
_

33:40.090 --> 33:43.826
[Alarm sounding]

33:43.861 --> 33:45.561
[Phone beeps]

33:45.629 --> 33:47.697
- [Rings]
- [Circuitry crackling]

33:47.731 --> 33:50.066
[Rings]

33:52.063 --> 33:55.946
_

33:55.971 --> 34:00.173
_

34:00.173 --> 34:03.181
_

34:04.381 --> 34:06.549
I can almost smell the sea air.

34:06.583 --> 34:08.184
I knew we'd make a sailor out of you.

34:17.127 --> 34:18.527
[Speaks Russian]

34:18.562 --> 34:20.263
[Guns cock]

34:20.297 --> 34:22.732
Stingray, this is Tiger Shark.
Are you in position?

34:22.766 --> 34:24.199
That's affirmative.

34:24.234 --> 34:27.003
Hang on.

34:27.036 --> 34:29.572
There's no way they haven't
checked our cells yet.

34:29.606 --> 34:31.074
Sir?

34:31.141 --> 34:32.708
No alarms.

34:32.743 --> 34:36.346
Not one call over the 1MC,
nothing over the radios?

34:36.380 --> 34:38.915
They're waiting for us on
the other side of that hatch.

34:38.949 --> 34:41.884
<i>The stern is blown. We need a
new way off this ship now.</i>

34:41.952 --> 34:44.219
Stingray, Tiger Shark.
Primary extract is blown.

34:44.254 --> 34:46.556
I repeat... Oscar is no good.

34:46.590 --> 34:49.092
[Panting]

34:53.092 --> 34:56.114
_

34:56.232 --> 34:58.027
_

34:58.145 --> 34:59.863
_

34:59.863 --> 35:01.381
_

35:01.381 --> 35:05.976
_

35:05.976 --> 35:08.378
Very clever, Commander.

35:08.445 --> 35:10.179
[Slams teacup down]

35:23.994 --> 35:26.963
[Man shouting in Russian]

35:33.036 --> 35:35.386
[Lowered voice] They're here. Let's go.
Let's go, let's go!

35:35.386 --> 35:36.672
[Man shouting in Russian]

35:36.673 --> 35:38.875
- Stay right there.
- [Shouting continues]

35:44.948 --> 35:46.182
- This way, ma'am.
- Come on, come on, come on.

35:46.216 --> 35:47.784
- Darling, be brave.
- Mom!

35:47.818 --> 35:50.353
- Stand there. Stand... Stand there.
- The ladder...

35:50.387 --> 35:52.989
- Get through.
- [Men shouting in distance]

35:53.056 --> 35:55.224
- [Panting]
- It's okay. Come with me.

36:09.573 --> 36:12.475
- [Gunfire]
- Get down! Stay down. Stay down!

36:12.509 --> 36:15.645
[Gunfire continues,
men shouting in Russian]

36:22.019 --> 36:25.588
[Shouting continues]

36:25.622 --> 36:26.923
[Gunshot]

36:30.093 --> 36:31.694
Clear!

36:37.581 --> 36:40.235
_

36:40.974 --> 36:43.774
_

