[Shouting in Russian]

36:59.864 --> 37:01.692
_

37:01.692 --> 37:05.629
_

37:05.629 --> 37:07.132
[Continues shouting in Russian]

37:07.132 --> 37:11.413
_

37:12.269 --> 37:15.104
- [Gunfire]
- Aah!

37:17.307 --> 37:18.608
[Shouting in Russian]

37:18.741 --> 37:24.505
_

37:27.784 --> 37:29.452
Got visual.

37:43.333 --> 37:45.334
Contact!

37:47.504 --> 37:49.872
[Grunting]

37:52.676 --> 37:54.477
Aah!

37:54.511 --> 37:55.945
Danny, do it!

37:55.979 --> 37:59.482
[Explosions]

38:02.185 --> 38:04.153
[Shouting in Russian]

38:04.187 --> 38:06.155
Aah!

38:07.858 --> 38:10.192
[Explosion]

38:13.864 --> 38:16.832
[Alarm sounding]

38:22.472 --> 38:24.040
[Rapid beeps]

38:24.074 --> 38:25.675
[Motor revving]

38:25.709 --> 38:27.443
[Explosion]

38:27.511 --> 38:30.813
[Breathing heavily]

38:34.351 --> 38:38.120
[Explosions]

38:48.365 --> 38:50.566
You rocked it, man!

38:50.601 --> 38:52.301
You really rocked it!

38:53.670 --> 38:56.439
We did it, sir.

38:56.473 --> 38:58.741
We did it.

38:58.775 --> 39:00.509
Cossetti!

39:01.878 --> 39:05.581
Cossetti! Talk to me, buddy, talk to me!

39:05.616 --> 39:06.983
He's been hit!

39:07.017 --> 39:09.952
Cossetti, come on! Stay with me!

39:09.987 --> 39:11.253
Hey!

39:17.060 --> 39:19.261
[Exhales deeply]

39:19.296 --> 39:21.430
[Knock on door]

39:21.465 --> 39:23.332
- Come in.
- [Door opens]

39:32.676 --> 39:34.610
[Door opens]

39:37.614 --> 39:40.082
Daddy! [Sobbing]

39:40.117 --> 39:42.718
Oh!

39:42.753 --> 39:45.955
[Sobbing]

